00:09:22.016 --> 00:09:25.870 align:middle line:90%


00:09:25.870 --> 00:09:28.510 align:middle line:84%
So one of the things that
I really want people to do

00:09:28.510 --> 00:09:30.760 align:middle line:84%
is completely ignore
the marketing of food.

00:09:30.760 --> 00:09:32.612 align:middle line:84%
All of the fancy
buzzwords they put

00:09:32.612 --> 00:09:33.820 align:middle line:90%
on the front of the package--

00:09:33.820 --> 00:09:37.090 align:middle line:84%
the low-fat, low-calorie,
gluten-free--

00:09:37.090 --> 00:09:39.040 align:middle line:84%
all of those things--
forget about it.

00:09:39.040 --> 00:09:40.870 align:middle line:84%
You have to look at
one thing and that

00:09:40.870 --> 00:09:42.730 align:middle line:90%
is the ingredients in food.

00:09:42.730 --> 00:09:45.040 align:middle line:84%
And if you don't
recognize an ingredient,

00:09:45.040 --> 00:09:47.200 align:middle line:84%
you need to put the
product back on the shelf

00:09:47.200 --> 00:09:49.060 align:middle line:90%
or learn about that ingredient.

00:09:49.060 --> 00:09:54.550 align:middle line:84%
And I think informed consumers
are the most beautiful part

00:09:54.550 --> 00:09:57.130 align:middle line:84%
of this catalyst of change
in the food revolution.

00:09:57.130 --> 00:10:01.900 align:middle line:84%
Because once you become aware
of how processed our food is

00:10:01.900 --> 00:10:04.210 align:middle line:84%
and what chemical
additives the food industry

00:10:04.210 --> 00:10:06.790 align:middle line:84%
has invented to
put in our foods,

00:10:06.790 --> 00:10:10.060 align:middle line:84%
you do not want to be part of
that experiment any longer.

00:10:10.060 --> 00:10:11.560 align:middle line:90%
You want to opt-out of that.

00:10:11.560 --> 00:10:13.930 align:middle line:84%
You don't want to bring in
those chemical additives

00:10:13.930 --> 00:10:16.030 align:middle line:90%
to your family every single day.

00:10:16.030 --> 00:10:19.240 align:middle line:84%
I'm about to be a mom
and I know I'm not

00:10:19.240 --> 00:10:22.450 align:middle line:84%
going to feed my child these
chemical additives that

00:10:22.450 --> 00:10:24.740 align:middle line:84%
have been invented
in the last 50 years,

00:10:24.740 --> 00:10:26.560 align:middle line:84%
largely to do one
thing, which is

00:10:26.560 --> 00:10:29.850 align:middle line:84%
to improve the bottom
line of the food industry.

00:10:29.850 --> 00:10:32.260 align:middle line:84%
They're not invented
to improve our health.

00:10:32.260 --> 00:10:35.020 align:middle line:84%
What I would like to do is
challenge the food scientists

00:10:35.020 --> 00:10:36.070 align:middle line:90%
of today.

00:10:36.070 --> 00:10:38.500 align:middle line:84%
Find ingredients and
find ways to make

00:10:38.500 --> 00:10:41.830 align:middle line:84%
food improve our health, not
just improve the bottom line.

00:10:41.830 --> 00:10:45.253 align:middle line:90%
